fields.name: CASIO Unisex Black Small Dial Analogue and Digital Watch
fields.description: Combining sleek dark looks with cool style, the Unisex Casio Classic Alarm Watch is a stylish performer.  The watch is 50-metre water resistant, so it’s fine to wear while out swimming. The domed spherical glass case adds an extra layer of protection if you’re exploring the depths. There’s a dual-time function as well as two types of alarm, an auto-calendar, and 60-hour stopwatch, so you’ll never miss an appointment.   The strong stainless-steel case houses a sleek jet-black dial with gold hour baton markers and luminous hands, as well as a digital display band across the bottom. The black rubber strap is durable and hardwearing, and provides the finishing touch to this stylish designer watch.

fields.name: CASIO G-Shock Men Black Digital Watch G-7710-1DR G223
fields.description: This Casio G-Shock Black Silver Men’s Alarm Chronograph Watch G-7700-1ER features a powerful and well structured display, with this robust styling being added to by multiple function buttons.  Features include a stop watch, world time function, calendar and a lap memory.

fields.name: CASIO EDIFICE Men Black Dial Chronograph Watch ED60
fields.description: Stylish Casio Edifice Chronograph watch, with a solid stainless steel case, water resistant to 100 metres, on a solid 5 link steel bracelet. Finishing the case is a black ion plated steel bezel, with tachymetre inscription. Matching the black bezel, is a black dial with silver subdial rings, with date window. Under the dial is a Japanese Quartz chronograph, with 12 hour measurement capability.

fields.name: ADIDAS Original Men Black Dial Chronograph Watch ADH2641
fields.description: Adidas Originals EDITION’s are great watches. Case is made out of Stainless Steel, which stands for a high quality of the item while the dial colour is Black. The watch is shipped with an original box and a guarantee from the manufacturer.

fields.description: Black ion-plated stainless steel case and bracelet (with compass set into bracelet). Fixed black ion-plated bezel. Black dial with black hands and stick hour markers. Arabic numerals mark the 3, 9 and 12 o'clock positions. Minute markers around the outer rim.

fields.name: Fossil Men Grey Dial Chronograph Watch FS4584
fields.description: The Grant FS4584 from Fossil is a gents fashion watch with a stainless steel bracelet. The FS4584 has a grey analogue dial with baton markers. The case of the Fossil FS4584 has a width of 44mm, excluding the crown, and has a thickness of 12mm. The case of the FS4584 is made from stainless steel and has a grey finish. The Fossil FS4584 has a stainless steel bracelet and fastens with a push-button three-fold clasp. The FS4584 is rated 50m water resistant (5 atmospheres) and suitable for swimming but not diving or snorkeling. The Fossil FS4584 also features; analogue chronograph. All of our watches are supplied in the manufacturer's packaging and with a full manufacturer's warranty.
